    <fr:title text="Quasi-separated spaces">Quasi-separated spaces</fr:title>
    <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>
  A topological space <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is <html:em>quasi-separated</html:em> if compact opens are closed under intersections.
</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
